<a name="closureresolution"></a>
	<div class="newstitle">April 2, 2020 - Closure Resolution</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class=""><p class="">During the April 2, 2020, emergency meeting, the Heber-Overgaard Unified School's Governing Board approved a resolution pertaining to school closure. Please take a moment to read the <a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_26195/site_26196/Documents/April-2-2020-School-Closure-Resolution.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">April 2, 2020, resolution announcement</a> for more information.</p></div></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem">
<a name="readbooksonline"></a>
	<div class="newstitle">Read Books Online!</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class="">
<p class="">Parents and Students,</p>
<p class="">RENAISSANCE is giving us the following information so we can read books online! Thank you, Mrs. Townsend, for reaching out to them! We appreciate the opportunity to continue to read! Please see the note from RENASISSANCE to Mrs. Townsend below. It provides the userid and password to access the online books.</p>
<p class="">Hello Mrs. Townsend,</p>
<p class="">As promised, here is the login information for your myON Shared Account, to share with your students:</p>
<p class=""></p>
<ul><li class="">
<a href="https://www.myon.com/school/readathome" title="" alt="" target="_blank">Login page</a><ul>
<li class="">School Name: Read at Home</li>
<li class="">Username: readnow</li>
<li class="">Password: myon</li>
</ul>
</li></ul>
<p class="">Also, <a href="http://go.renaissance.com/NJ00ePBt000u0dD10Pj0g3o" title="" alt="" target="_blank">check out this quick video tour</a>.</p>
<p class="">Questions or trouble logging in? Our teams are here to support you and your students during this challenging time, so please do not hesitate to contact us. Weâ€™re here to help.</p>
<p class="">Sincerely,</p>
<p class="">Renaissance<br>(800) 338-4204<br><a href="mailto:answers@renaissance.com" title="" alt="" target="_top">answers@renaissance.com</a></p>
</div></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem">
<a name="information"></a>
	<div class="newstitle">Important Information Access</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class=""><div class="">
<div class="">Parents, staff, and community members can now receive important information and updates on items such as school delays or cancellations due to snow by calling (928) 535-4622 and pressing 1 for important announcements.</div>
<div class=""><br></div>
<div class="">We also encourage you to listen to one of the local radio stations for school information regarding weather:</div>
<div class=""><br></div>
<div class=""><ul>
<li class="">FM Stations: 92.1 - 92.5 - 93.5 - 95.7 - 96.5 - 101.7</li>
<li class="">AM Station: 1450</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div></div>
</div>

